name: Omega Ouzeri
description: Greece in Seattle! Omega Ouzeri is open for dine-in, takeout and delivery for Dinner. We opened our blue door on Capitol Hill, in 2015, to share authentic and contemporary Greek food with Seattle. We redefine traditional Greek recipes made from great vegetables and fresh seafood, around the long-standing tradition of mezedes - small portions, of exceptional food, to be shared by everyone around the table. Yia Yia's inspiration for the next generation. With a full bar and an award winning, Greek only, wine list, Omega is the most authentic Greek experience in the Pacific Northwest. With a wide range of Tsipouro and Ouzo to add character to our seafood offerings, you will be wowed and ready to book your trip to Greece!
